*brasero-0.5.2 (27 Feb 2007)

  27 Feb 2007; Luis Medinas <metalgod@gentoo.org> +brasero-0.5.2.ebuild:
  Version Bump. New Homepage. Remove older this is a bug fix release. Drop
  ~ppc keyword due libisofs lack of keyword for this arch.

  24 Jan 2007; Marius Mauch <genone@gentoo.org> brasero-0.4.4.ebuild,
  brasero-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Replacing einfo with elog

  13 Jan 2007; nixnut <nixnut@gentoo.org> brasero-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc wrt bug 156453

  27 Nov 2006; Luis Medinas <metalgod@gentoo.org> brasero-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Added libburn support and remove libnotify since it won't be used by this
  stable series. Drop ~ppc keyword because libburn needs to be keyworded.

  18 Nov 2006; Luis Medinas <metalgod@gentoo.org> brasero-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Use gnome-mount instead of pmount fixes bug #155569.

